description:
With offices in Federal Way and Tacoma, the attorneys at Park Chenaur & Associates, Inc., provide unmatched advocacy and support to clients throughout Western Washington and the surrounding areas of the greater Sea-Tac region who suffered an injury or lost a loved one due to someone else's negligence or wrongdoing.

Over the course of our history, our law firm's top-rated, award-winning attorneys have achieved remarkable success fighting for the rights and entitlements of innocent accident victims and their families. To date, we have recovered more than $50 million in total compensation for our plaintiff clients, and we promise to do all we can to increase your chances of obtaining the maximum amount of compensation you deserve.

Backed by more than 20 years of combined legal experience, our lawyers have successfully handled more than 10,000 personal injury and wrongful death cases in our area. We have also received five-star client reviews on Facebook and Google along with numerous testimonials and referrals from our satisfied clients. What's more, our attorneys have earned Top 100 Trial Lawyer designations from the National Trial Lawyers along with many other top rankings and endorsements from our peers.

With an additional law office in Tacoma, Park Chenaur & Associates, Inc., provides convenient access to the quality, effective legal representation you need when you need it the most. To begin the process, you can call our law office or visit our website to schedule a free initial consultation, and we also offer virtual consultations to help keep you safe and healthy in these uncertain times.
